sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Edge
    participant UI as Streamlit UI<br/>8501/TCP HTTP
    participant API as Backend API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant LLM as Ollama LLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Catalog as RHOAI Model Catalog<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 1: Conversational Recommendation Pipeline

    User->>Route: HTTPS POST /recommend<br/>TLS Edge Termination
    Route->>UI: HTTP :8501
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/recommend<br/>HTTP :8000 (cluster-internal)

    Note over API: Step 1: Intent Extraction
    API->>LLM: POST /api/chat<br/>HTTP :11434 (no auth)
    LLM-->>API: Extracted intent JSON<br/>(model, use_case, constraints)

    Note over API: Step 2: Specification Generation
    API->>HF: GET /api/models/{model}<br/>HTTPS :443, Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>API: Model config<br/>(architecture, params, quant)

    Note over API: Step 3: Configuration Finding
    API->>PG: SQL Query<br/>TCP :5432 (password auth)
    Note over PG: Filter configs by SLO constraints<br/>(TTFT, ITL, E2E latency @ p95)
    PG-->>API: Matching GPU configurations

    Note over API: Step 4: Multi-Criteria Scoring
    Note over API: Score across 5 dimensions:<br/>accuracy(40%), cost(40%),<br/>latency(10%), complexity(10%)

    Note over API: Step 5: Deployment YAML Generation
    Note over API: Render Jinja2 templates:<br/>InferenceService + HPA + ServiceMonitor

    API-->>UI: Ranked recommendations<br/>(5 views: accuracy, cost, latency, simple, balanced)
    UI-->>Route: HTML response with tabs
    Route-->>User: Recommendation dashboard

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 2: Model Catalog Sync (Background Daemon)

    Note over API: On startup when<br/>PLANNER_BENCHMARK_SOURCE=model_catalog
    API->>Catalog: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/models<br/>HTTPS :8443, Bearer Token (SA)
    Catalog-->>API: Validated models + performance artifacts
    API->>PG: INSERT benchmark rows<br/>(deduplicated via config_id hash)
    Note over PG: Idempotent sync

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 3: Cluster Deployment

    User->>Route: HTTPS POST /deploy-to-cluster
    Route->>UI: HTTP :8501
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/deploy-to-cluster<br/>HTTP :8000
    API->>K8s: POST InferenceService CR<br/>HTTPS :6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>API: Created InferenceService
    API-->>UI: Deployment status + ID
    UI-->>Route: Deployment confirmation
    Route-->>User: Deployment dashboard

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 3b: Deployment Monitoring

    User->>Route: HTTPS GET /deployments/{id}/k8s-status
    Route->>API: HTTP :8000
    API->>K8s: GET InferenceService status<br/>HTTPS :6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>API: InferenceService conditions
    API-->>Route: Status response
    Route-->>User: Live deployment status
